2. exact summary of changes

In [data/architecture_selected/active_architecture.json](/home/meta_os/MapleWorld/data/architecture_selected/active_architecture.json#L16), changed `variant.control_parameters.potion_sink_pressure` from `0.25` to `0.258`.

In [data/design_graph/economy.json](/home/meta_os/MapleWorld/data/design_graph/economy.json#L94), added the explicit economy graph node `economy.potion_sink_pressure` under the `economy` domain so this selected sink knob is surfaced in the shard.

In [ops/codex_state/progress.json](/home/meta_os/MapleWorld/ops/codex_state/progress.json#L5), added `selected_balance_adjustment: "potion_sink_pressure=0.258"` to record this bounded balance adjustment in progress state.

3. verification performed

Parsed all three edited JSON files successfully with `python3 json.load(...)`.

Confirmed `potion_sink_pressure` now resolves to `0.258` in the active selected architecture.

Confirmed `economy.potion_sink_pressure` exists in the economy design graph.

